    <section class="about-intro">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-intro-content">
                <div class="about-intro-image">
                    <img src="/ImageStyle/craftman.jpg" alt="Furniture craftsman at work">
                </div>
                <div class="about-intro-text">
                    <h2>Artisans of Elegant Living</h2>
                    <p>Aurora Home was founded with a simple yet profound vision: to create furniture that transforms houses into homes. Our journey began in a small workshop with just three craftsmen who shared a passion for woodworking and design.</p>
                    <p>Today, we've grown into a team of dedicated artisans, designers, and furniture enthusiasts who continue to honor traditional craftsmanship while embracing modern aesthetics and sustainable practices.</p>
                    <div class="signature">
                        <img src="/ImageStyle/signature.jpg" alt="Founder's signature">
                        <p>Emma Richardson, Founder</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="our-values">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Values</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">The principles that guide everything we do</p>
            
            <div class="values-grid">
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-gem"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Quality Craftsmanship</h3>
                    <p>We believe in creating furniture that stands the test of time. Each piece is crafted with meticulous attention to detail using the finest materials and time-honored techniques.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Sustainability</h3>
                    <p>Our commitment to the environment is reflected in our responsibly sourced materials, eco-friendly production processes, and durable designs that reduce waste.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-paint-brush"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Timeless Design</h3>
                    <p>We create pieces that transcend fleeting trends. Our designs blend classic elegance with contemporary sensibilities for furniture that remains relevant year after year.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Customer Focus</h3>
                    <p>Your satisfaction is our priority. We're dedicated to providing exceptional service and creating furniture that enhances your living spaces and daily life.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="our-process">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Process</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">From concept to creation</p>
            
            <div class="process-timeline">
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Design</h3>
                        <p>Our designers draw inspiration from nature, architecture, and timeless furniture traditions to create pieces that are both beautiful and functional.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Material Selection</h3>
                        <p>We carefully source the finest sustainably harvested woods, premium fabrics, and quality hardware to ensure longevity and beauty.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Crafting</h3>
                        <p>Our skilled artisans combine traditional woodworking techniques with modern precision to bring each design to life with exceptional attention to detail.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Finishing</h3>
                        <p>Each piece receives multiple layers of hand-applied finishes that protect the wood while enhancing its natural beauty and ensuring a flawless appearance.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">5</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Quality Control</h3>
                        <p>Before any piece leaves our workshop, it undergoes rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for quality and craftsmanship.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

